{"tid":1866410,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你班連登仔我忍無可忍","createTime":"2020-02-06T17:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T02:08:08.000Z","uid":299756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"978c4cdb521ef7dcdb8eee3983312b3b8b53996a","tid":1866410,"uid":299756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T17:29:11.000Z","msg":"屌你地 今日係醫護最後一日罷工 成個熱門唔好話推 提都唔多見人提 <br />\n<br />\n今日班醫護就要投票繼唔繼續罷工 知唔知已經有幾多醫護想放棄唔罷<br />\n<br />\n但係林奠當班人係condom <br />\n但係其實佢地咩都爭取唔到<br />\n知唔知幾多人下星期就要入dirty team  <br />\n知唔知幾多人已經比人秋後算帳<br />\n知唔知宜家佢地物資有幾短缺<br />\n知唔知佢地入去係送死<br />\n<br />\n如果你有少少良心 唔該推我個post出去 公海又好咩都好 所有醫護唔該 勿忘初衷 唔撚好同我放棄 你地都係人命 醫護五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"e80edb9776fba5b9985409282edffbab29abbcc3","tid":1866410,"uid":319616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T17:32:05.000Z","msg":"黑警比人影到係警車交收CSI口罩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1866377\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1866377</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"88ad4a3879f9674c6b196b8843f5744ad7bcb829","tid":1866410,"uid":299756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T02:06:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51266585968e80c2a1c76a010a05971423cc35d8","tid":1866410,"uid":299756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T02:06:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0f3e0c92a7047c1d23b7c91117d7f018d35a3e","tid":1866410,"uid":299756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T02:06:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48d2b9bdb3e0c16900e35630995f095c8562887","tid":1866410,"uid":299756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T02:07:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/